info: Rating, 5 stars,  · March 2023,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment:
The host, Junayed, is a very nice and kind person. He sent me some messages before I arrived to make sure that I could check in smoothly.
His wife was very lovely and kind, too. They helped me when I needed .
The place was very clean with a private room and bathroom.
It was a totally pleasant stay. I would absolutely stay with them if I come back.
